'''華裔泰國人'''{{efn|本社群已同化屬於[[暹罗泰族|泰人]]的一支，不自稱为華人或泰国华人}}（{{lang-th|ชาวไทยเชื้อสายจีน}}），口語也稱'''空恭貼'''{{efn|由於華裔泰國人就是[[曼谷都會區|首都圈]]的[[原住民|原住民]]，指首都圈與泰國中部地區的當地文化不通，故他們稱呼[[泰族|暹羅泰族]]為'''中部泰國人'''<small>（{{lang-th|คนภาคกลาง}}）</small>為了區別，請見[[首都泰語|首都泰語]]。}}（{{lang-th|คนกรุงเทพ}}；字意：曼谷人），指移民到[[泰國|泰國]]的[[華人|華裔]]。融入泰族後，屬於[[暹罗泰族|泰人]]的一支，有约900万人，是泰国规模最大的少数族裔群体，亦是规模最大的[[華僑華人|華僑華人]]群体，占泰国总人口的11%至14%<ref name="Springer">{{cite journal |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/330368922 |author1=John Draper |author2=Joel Sawat Selway |title=A New Dataset on Horizontal Structural Ethnic Inequalities in Thailand in Order to Address Sustainable Development Goal 10 |journal=Social Indicators Research |page=280 |volume=141 |issue=4 |date=January 2019 |doi=10.1007/s11205-019-02065-4 |s2cid=149845432 |access-date=2020-02-06}}</ref><ref name="Theraphan">{{Cite book |editor-last1=Guan |editor-first1=Lee Hock |editor-last2=Suryadinata |editor-first2=Leo Suryadinata |last=Luangthongkum |first=Theraphan |chapter=The Position of Non-Thai Languages in Thailand |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ImjVqAVxO74C&pg=PA191 |title=Language, Nation and Development in Southeast Asia |publisher=ISEAS Publishing |year=2007 |page=191 |isbn=9789812304827 |via=Google Books |access-date=2021-11-08 |archive-date=2022-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220303065325/https://books.google.com/books?id=ImjVqAVxO74C&pg=PA191 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="West794">{{citation |author=Barbara A. West |title=Encyclopedia of the Peoples of Asia and Oceania |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pCiNqFj3MQsC&pg=PA794 |publisher=Facts on File |year=2009 |page=794 |isbn=978-1438119137 |via=Google Books |accessdate=2021-11-08 |archive-date=2021-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108181658/https://books.google.com/books?id=pCiNqFj3MQsC&pg=PA794 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其中相當一部份來自[[中國|中國]][[廣東|廣東]][[潮汕地區|潮汕地區]]<ref name="Baker-2009">{{cite book |last1=Baker |first1=Chris |last2=Phongpaichit |first2=Pasuk |title=A History of Thailand |date=2009 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |isbn=9780521759151 |edition=2nd, paper}}</ref>{{RP|93}}。

华裔泰国人已高度融入泰国社会，当今泰国王室[[扎克里王朝|扎克里王朝]]亦有华裔血统<ref name="RamaI">{{cite book|last1=Reid|first1=Anthony|title=A History of Southeast Asia: Critical Crossroads|year=2015|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=cETJBgAAQBAJ&q=chakri+dynasty+chinese+mon&pg=PA215|page=215|isbn=9780631179610|access-date=2021-11-08|archive-date=2021-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108181658/https://books.google.com/books?id=cETJBgAAQBAJ&q=chakri+dynasty+chinese+mon&pg=PA215|dead-url=no}}</ref>。华裔和本土泰人通婚的现象很普遍，混血后代多同化为泰人，以[[泰语|泰语]]为母语<ref>{{cite news |last1=Jiangtao |first1=Shi |title=Time of uncertainty lies ahead for Bangkok's ethnic Chinese |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/southeast-asia/article/2028412/time-uncertainty-lies-ahead-bangkoks-ethnic-chinese |access-date=2020-04-28 |work=South China Morning Post |date=2016-10-16 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809194635/https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/southeast-asia/article/2028412/time-uncertainty-lies-ahead-bangkoks-ethnic-chinese |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Gambe-2000>{{Cite book |title=Overseas Chinese Entrepreneurship and Capitalist Development in Southeast Asia |last=Gambe |first=Annabelle |year= 2000 |publisher=Palgrave Macmillan|isbn=978-0312234966}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chaloemtiarana |first1=Thak |title=Are We Them? Textual and Literary Representations of the Chinese in Twentieth-Century Thailand |journal=Southeast Asian Studies |date=2014-12-25 |volume=3 |issue=3 |url=https://englishkyoto-seas.org/2014/12/vol-3-no-3-thak-chaloemtiarana/ |access-date=2020-04-28 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614081729/https://englishkyoto-seas.org/2014/12/vol-3-no-3-thak-chaloemtiarana/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於華人族群已普遍泰化，大多數華人已喪失中文能力<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2/20191112-%E6%9B%BE%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E8%8F%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%B0%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8C%96 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-03-27 |archive-date=2022-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220319001142/https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2/20191112-%E6%9B%BE%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E8%8F%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%B0%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8C%96 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。华裔泰国人居于泰国的中等阶层，势力遍及泰国社会各个方面<ref name="Smith-2005">{{cite journal |last1=Smith |first1=Anthony |title=Thailand's Security and the Sino-Thai Relationship |journal=China Brief |date=2005-02-01 |volume=5 |issue=3 |url=https://jamestown.org/program/thailands-security-and-the-sino-thai-relationship/ |access-date=2020-04-29 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808104636/https://jamestown.org/program/thailands-security-and-the-sino-thai-relationship/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Jiangtao |first1=Shi |title=In Bangkok's Chinatown, grief and gratitude following Thai king's death |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy-defence/article/2028246/bangkoks-chinatown-grief-and-gratitude-following-thai |access-date=2020-04-29 |work=South China Morning Post |date=2016-10-14 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808195606/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy-defence/article/2028246/bangkoks-chinatown-grief-and-gratitude-following-thai |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=budNEqARJBAC&q=chinese+southeast+asia+percent+control&pg=PT15 |title=The Dragon Network: Inside Stories of the Most Successful Chinese Family |author1=A. B. Susanto |last2=Susa |first2=Patricia |publisher=Wiley |date=2013 |access-date=2014-12-02 |isbn=9781118339404 |archive-date=2021-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108181702/https://books.google.com/books?id=budNEqARJBAC&q=chinese+southeast+asia+percent+control&pg=PT15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="google1">{{cite book |url = https:/